creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
Happy Hours Market est une startup qui se charge de collecter quotidiennement les invendus des supermarchés.
Les produits récoltés sont ensuite revendus à moitié prix via l’application, permettant ainsi aux citoyens qui le souhaitent de s’impliquer dans la lutte contre le gaspillage alimentaire tout en faisant des économies.

Par ailleurs, une grande partie des invendus collectés sont livrés gratuitement à des associations caritatives qui viennent en aide aux plus démunis.
descriptionShort: Your half-price shopping to fight waste.

Bravo pour votre lutte contre le gaspi ! Nous continuons d’améliorer notre application pour répondre à vos demandes et résoudre les bugs existants.

Dans cette mise à jour, nous avons travaillé sur :

Merci pour votre confiance et à bientôt au Happy Truck !

L’équipe HHM

title: Happy Hours Market

creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
Rejoins l’aventure antigaspi tout en faisant des économies !  Tous les soirs, de 19h30 à 21h, les invendus des magasins de ton quartier sont disponibles à moitié prix sur l’App. Inscris-toi gratuitement et rejoins la communauté des "Happiers". Nous sommes déjà plus de 10.000 inscrits !

Comment ça marche?
Tous les soirs, nos camions réfrigérés récupèrent l’excédent alimentaire des magasins de ton quartier.
- À 19h30, les produits récoltés sont disponibles à moitié prix sur l’App.
- Choisis ton point de retrait, puis sélectionne tes produits préférés.
- Entre 20h et 21h, récupère ta commande le soir même à côté de chez toi.
- A 21h, une grande partie des invendus collectés sont livrés gratuitement à des associations caritatives qui viennent en aide aux plus démunis.
 
Ensemble, mettons fin au gaspillage alimentaire.
descriptionShort: Your half-price shopping to fight waste.

L’équipe Happy Hours Market

title: Happy Hours Market

creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
📍 Brussels and Namur (Belgium)

Join the food waste fight while saving money! Every evening, from 7:30 p.m. to 9 p.m., unsold products from supermarkets in your neighborhood are available at half price on the App.

Sign up for free and join the "Happiers" community. We are more than 20.000 people !

How does it work ?
Every afternoon, our yellow trucks collect surplus food from supermarkets in your neighborhood.
- At 7:30 p.m., the products collected are available at half price on the App.
- Choose your pick-up point and select your favorite products.
- Pick up your order the same evening between 8 p.m. and 9 p.m.
- At 9 p.m., a large part of the unsold products are delivered free of charge to charities helping the people in need.

Together, let's end food waste.
descriptionShort: Your groceries at half the price to win the food waste fight

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
In this release we worked on a new design of the App to improve the user experience. Your orders and vouchers are now more accessible!
We also improved the performance of the App, the payment system and fixed a few bugs.
Thank you for your trust and see you soon at the Happy Truck !

title: Happy Hours Market

creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
📍 Brussels and Namur (Belgium)

Join the food waste fight while saving money ! Every day, surplus food from supermarkets in your neighborhood is available at half the price on the App.

Sign up for free and join the "Happiers" community. We are more than 20.000 people !

How does it work ?
Every day, our yellow trucks collect unsold food from supermarkets in your neighborhood.
- At 7:30 p.m., the products collected are available at half the price on the App.
- Select your pick-up point and check the opening hours !

- Choose your favorite products and make your order.
- Pick up your order the same day.
- At 9 p.m., a large part of the unsold products is delivered free of charge to charities helping the people in need.

title:
Happy Hours Market
7.1.2

creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
Save money

Save money by fighting food waste! Enjoy daily discounts on tasty anti-waste products thanks to our partnerships with quality stores. Fill your fridge with delicious products at low price while preserving the environment.

Shop responsibly and fight food waste

A third of the world's food production ends up in the garbage. In Belgium, nearly 7 tonnes of food waste are thrown away every minute!

By shopping at Happy Hours Market, you prevent unsold products from supermarket and retailers from ending up in the garbage, saving nearly one ton of fresh food every day.

Simplify your shopping

Every day, order delicious food at low prices. Select the products you want from the e-shop, then pick up your order at the nearest collection point in Brussels region.

Join a community of Happiers

More than 50,000 customers and fans are registered on the app. Download the app and join the community of Happiers! Together, let's end food waste in Brussels.
descriptionShort: Fight food waste at discount

title:
Happy Hours Market
7.6.7

creator: HappyHoursMarket
descriptionHtml:
Save money doing your groceries while fighting food waste with Happy Hours Market

Did you know that 1/3 of global food production is thrown away? This is mainly due to distributors getting rid of their unsold goods long before their expiration date. Doing your groceries at Happy Hours Market means saving delicious products from waste and saving nearly €800 per year!

How does it work?

- Sign up for free on the app
- Select your pickup point (available in Brussels region)
- Choose the products you want with just a few clicks (no bad surprises 😉)
- Pick up your order the day you choose.

Thanks to our partners engaged in fighting food waste, Happy Hours Market offers daily discounts on tasty unsold products. Every day, more than 5,000 products are collected and uploaded online, ready to be consumed during the week or to be frozen.

Download the app and join a community of over 50.000 "Happiers."

For any questions & suggestions, contact: [info@happyhours.be](mailto:info@happyhours.be)
descriptionShort: Anti foodwaste tips
